Class ParametersAmong

    • builder.constraints.parameters.ConstraintParameters

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Allocable, Freeable
    public class ParametersAmong
extends ConstraintParameters
    ParametersAmong
    Parameters of the Among constraint.
    Contains the set of values that are constrained, the size of the window (q), and the min. and max. number of occurrences.
